OL,6,FA "prolific" predator who groomed
OL,7,Fyoung girls on social media before
OL,8,Fassaulting them is facing a long jail
OL,9,Fsentence after being found guilty of
OL,10,Frape and a string of sexual offences.
OL,12,FPhilip Hamer, 34, was charged in March
OL,13,F2024 with sexual offences against
OL,14,Feight victims between 2010 and 2023.
