OL,4,Craped young girls
OL,6,FHamer had already admitted several
OL,7,Foffences but following a trial at
OL,8,FManchester Crown Court, he was found
OL,9,Fguilty of a further 21 charges,
OL,10,Fincluding eight counts of rape; seven
OL,11,Fcounts of sexual assault; six counts
OL,12,Fof causing or inciting a child to
OL,13,Fengage in sexual activity; and one
OL,14,Fcount of sexual activity with a child.
OL,16,FDetectives found that he used social
OL,17,Fmedia apps to target and make contact
OL,18,Fwith his victims by manipulating and
OL,19,Fgrooming them.
