OL,4,Craped young girls
OL,6,FMany of Hamer's victims were teenagers
OL,7,Fat the time they were abused. After
OL,8,Fone victim came forward, Hamer's phone
OL,9,Fwas seized which enabled police to
OL,10,Ftrace further victims.
OL,12,FHamer, of Birchfield Drive, Worsley,
OL,13,Fiincited his victims to send him
OL,14,Fhundreds of pictures and videos over a
OL,15,Fperiod of seven years.
OL,17,FOfficers later found voyeuristic
OL,18,Fvideos and pictures Hamer had taken of
OL,19,Fpeople in changing rooms who were not
OL,20,Faware they were being filmed.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
