OL,3,C'Prolific' sex offender groomed and
OL,4,Craped young girls
OL,6,FGreater Manchester Police Detective
OL,7,FConstable Denise Garde said: "Firstly,
OL,8,FI would like to commend the bravery of
OL,9,Fthose victims who came forward and
OL,10,Freported their abuse to us.
OL,12,F"Time is no barrier when it comes to
OL,13,Fbeing sexually abused ` no matter how
OL,14,Flong ago it was, or old you were at
OL,15,Fthe time, we will listen to you.
OL,17,F"Hamer managed to instil fear in his
OL,18,Fvictims - he was much older than them,
OL,19,Fhe offered them lifts in his car so he
OL,20,Fknew where they lived.
