OL,6,F"He groomed the victims and survivors
OL,7,Fat the centre of their case, instilled
OL,8,Ffear, and exploited their
OL,9,Fvulnerabilities.
OL,11,F"It took one brave victim to come
OL,12,Fforward, speak to our officers and
OL,13,Fdetail their abuse. This opened up the
OL,14,Fwhole case and resulted in us
OL,15,Fobtaining evidence that Hamer was a
OL,16,Fprolific sex offender."
OL,18,FHamer was found guilty of 33 charges
OL,19,Fby a jury at a trial which concluded
OL,20,Fon Friday, 29 November 2024.
